        "page": "158",
        "text": "Exetutive Summary p, _-,__ , Company Snapshot Super Star Car Wash (\"Super Star\" or \"the Company\") is the operator of one of the pre-eminent car wash chains in several of the hottest markets in the US. Founded in 1993, the Company has grown to 33 sites, each exhibiting strong financial results and growth potential. With over two decades of operational experience, Management has positioned the Company to be one of the most profitable and recognized names in the markets it serves. The vast majority of the Company's locations are Express Wash only, while a small number of Full Service sites have been strategically located to serve a broad range of Super Star customers looking for enhanced service offerings. Express Wash represented roughly 90% of car wash revenue in 2021 LTM through May (Full Service represented 10%). The Company benefits from recurring monthly members under its \"Fast Pass\" system, which has been growing sizably under Management's strategic guidance and represented 59% of car wash revenue in the LTM period. Sites utilize state-of- the-art tunnels and washing equipment paired with courteous and reliable customer service, establishing the Company's reputation as one of the top wash providers in the US. Prospects for additional growth remain vibrant, both in terms of new locations and customer acquisition at current facilities. To further expand market share, the Company continues to identify suitable land and develop additional sites. Super Star's operational excellence along with its strong branding will allow the business to continue outperforming competitors in the markets of Phoenix, San Diego, and California's Inland Empire, as well as new markets it enters including Denver. Million Cars (2018-2021 LTM) (2018-2021 LTM) ($ millions) 2021 LTM 2021 FY 2022 FY Revenue $97.3 109.3 170.4 Pro Forma EBITDA $32.0 39.0 67.2 Margin 32.9% 35.7% 39.5% LTM represents pro forma numbers as of May 2021. As of 2021 LTM May. Gross Profit Mix \u2022 Convenience Store Strictly Private and Confidential 6"
